The paper also discusses the interplay between convergence rate and estimation accuracy, which is related to control systems and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper includes simulations to support the theoretical findings, which is related to computational mathematics, making cs.MA (Mathematical Software) a possible sub-category.
